These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, disaster
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, car
1. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the car is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action |
| Transport     | car    | bus   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
City: liverpool, colone
House: cottage, victorian
1. the cottage house is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| City   | colone | liverpool        |
| House      | cottage  | victorian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
City: colone, boston
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, surfing
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| City   | boston    | colone |
| Sport   | tennis | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, documentary
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, february
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance      | documentary |
| Birthday       | december | february    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
