.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-8::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, writer
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, old-henry
1. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the manager is on the left of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Job   | manager | writer |
| Cigar           | old-henry       | cain       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-9::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, bike
1. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |
| Beverage           | tea | sprite |
| Transport   | bike | van    |

