The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, indie
1. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Birthday   | april | july   |
| Music-Genre         | funk | indie |

